sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Team Leader
    participant FE as React<br/>TeamPage
    participant API as DRF<br/>RemoveMemberView
    participant Perm as IsTeamLeader
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: Click "Remove" on team member
    FE->>FE: Show confirmation dialog
    U->>FE: Confirm removal
    FE->>API: DELETE /api/environments/{env_id}/members/{user_id}/remove/
    API->>Perm: has_permission(request)
    Perm-->>API: Allowed (Team Leader role)
    API->>DB: EnvironmentMembership.objects.get(user=user_id, environment=env)
    DB-->>API: Membership instance
    API->>DB: membership.delete()
    DB-->>API: Membership removed
    API-->>FE: 204 No Content
    FE-->>U: Member removed from team list
